{
  "stem": "4189.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I used to sleep in the bakery right on the benches where we used to bake the bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I used to sleep there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this went on for awhile, and then two friends that appealed to the authorities-- we were finally able to get those ration cards.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Which was, then, a big help because at least we were able to buy the meager rations that they were giving out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And after a while, in 19-- this was still in 1940, 41.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in May of 1942, they started to-- already in the beginning of 1942, they started to impose the same laws against the Jews that they did in Germany.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You had to wear a Jewish star, a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you had to change your names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You had to-- for instance, my name was Herman Haller, I had to be called Abraham.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "All men, all males had to be called Abraham, and all females had to be called Sarah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They had to add that to their name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Like my mother, for instance, her name was Anna.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So her name was Anna Sarah Haller.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so they imposed all these so-called Nuremberg Laws.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They called them Nuremberg Laws because these laws were initiated from the town of Nuremberg in Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
